## üé® Design Requirements

### Color System (D·ª±a tr√™n Figma)
```css
:root {
  /* Primary Colors */
  --rb-primary-50: #eff6ff;
  --rb-primary-100: #dbeafe;
  --rb-primary-500: #3b82f6;
  --rb-primary-600: #2563eb;
  --rb-primary-900: #1e3a8a;
  
  /* Gray Scale */
  --rb-gray-50: #f9fafb;
  --rb-gray-100: #f3f4f6;
  --rb-gray-200: #e5e7eb;
  --rb-gray-300: #d1d5db;
  --rb-gray-400: #9ca3af;
  --rb-gray-500: #6b7280;
  --rb-gray-600: #4b5563;
  --rb-gray-700: #374151;
  --rb-gray-800: #1f2937;
  --rb-gray-900: #111827;
  
  /* Semantic Colors */
  --rb-success: #10b981;
  --rb-warning: #f59e0b;
  --rb-error: #ef4444;
  --rb-info: #3b82f6;
}
```

### Typography Scale
```css
:root {
  /* Font Family */
  --rb-font-sans: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  
  /* Font Sizes */
  --rb-text-xs: 0.75rem;     /* 12px */
  --rb-text-sm: 0.875rem;    /* 14px */
  --rb-text-base: 1rem;      /* 16px */
  --rb-text-lg: 1.125rem;    /* 18px */
  --rb-text-xl: 1.25rem;     /* 20px */
  --rb-text-2xl: 1.5rem;     /* 24px */
  --rb-text-3xl: 1.875rem;   /* 30px */
  --rb-text-4xl: 2.25rem;    /* 36px */
  
  /* Font Weights */
  --rb-font-normal: 400;
  --rb-font-medium: 500;
  --rb-font-semibold: 600;
  --rb-font-bold: 700;
}
```

### Spacing System
```css
:root {
  --rb-space-0: 0;
  --rb-space-1: 0.25rem;   /* 4px */
  --rb-space-2: 0.5rem;    /* 8px */
  --rb-space-3: 0.75rem;   /* 12px */
  --rb-space-4: 1rem;      /* 16px */
  --rb-space-5: 1.25rem;   /* 20px */
  --rb-space-6: 1.5rem;    /* 24px */
  --rb-space-8: 2rem;      /* 32px */
  --rb-space-10: 2.5rem;   /* 40px */
  --rb-space-12: 3rem;     /* 48px */
  --rb-space-16: 4rem;     /* 64px */
}
```

## üß± Core Components C·∫ßn T·∫°o

### 1. Buttons
```html
<!-- Primary Button -->
<button class="rb-btn rb-btn-primary">Primary Button</button>
<button class="rb-btn rb-btn-primary rb-btn-lg">Large Primary</button>
<button class="rb-btn rb-btn-primary" disabled>Disabled</button>

<!-- Secondary Button -->
<button class="rb-btn rb-btn-secondary">Secondary Button</button>

<!-- Icon Button -->
<button class="rb-btn rb-btn-icon">
  <svg>...</svg>
</button>
```

### 2. Form Elements
```html
<!-- Input Field -->
<div class="rb-form-group">
  <label class="rb-label">Email Address</label>
  <input type="email" class="rb-input" placeholder="Enter email">
  <span class="rb-error-message">This field is required</span>
</div>

<!-- Select Dropdown -->
<div class="rb-form-group">
  <label class="rb-label">Location</label>
  <select class="rb-select">
    <option>Choose location</option>
    <option>Downtown Branch</option>
  </select>
</div>

<!-- Textarea -->
<div class="rb-form-group">
  <label class="rb-label">Special Requests</label>
  <textarea class="rb-textarea" rows="4"></textarea>
</div>
```

### 3. Cards
```html
<!-- Basic Card -->
<div class="rb-card">
  <div class="rb-card-header">
    <h3 class="rb-card-title">Card Title</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="rb-card-body">
    <p>Card content goes here</p>
  </div>
</div>

