  <div class="rb-stat-icon">
    <svg>...</svg>
  </div>
  <div class="rb-stat-content">
    <div class="rb-stat-number">24</div>
    <div class="rb-stat-label">Today's Bookings</div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### 4. Modal Structure
```html
<div class="rb-modal-overlay">
  <div class="rb-modal">
    <div class="rb-modal-header">
      <h2 class="rb-modal-title">Modal Title</h2>
      <button class="rb-modal-close">&times;</button>
    </div>
    <div class="rb-modal-body">
      <!-- Content -->
    </div>
    <div class="rb-modal-footer">
      <button class="rb-btn rb-btn-secondary">Cancel</button>
      <button class="rb-btn rb-btn-primary">Confirm</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### 5. Navigation
