## üåô Dark Mode System

### CSS Variables for Dark Mode
```css
/* Light Mode (Default) */
:root {
  --rb-bg-primary: #ffffff;
  --rb-bg-secondary: #f9fafb;
  --rb-text-primary: #111827;
  --rb-text-secondary: #6b7280;
  --rb-border: #e5e7eb;
}

/* Dark Mode */
[data-theme="dark"] {
  --rb-bg-primary: #1f2937;
  --rb-bg-secondary: #111827;
  --rb-text-primary: #f9fafb;
  --rb-text-secondary: #d1d5db;
  --rb-border: #374151;
}
```

### Theme Toggle Component
```html
<button class="rb-theme-toggle" id="themeToggle">
  <svg class="rb-theme-icon rb-sun-icon"><!-- Sun SVG --></svg>
  <svg class="rb-theme-icon rb-moon-icon"><!-- Moon SVG --></svg>
</button>
```

## üì± Responsive Breakpoints
```css
:root {
  --rb-screen-sm: 640px;
  --rb-screen-md: 768px;
  --rb-screen-lg: 1024px;
  --rb-screen-xl: 1280px;
}

/* Mobile First Approach */
.rb-container {
  padding: var(--rb-space-4);
}

@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .rb-container {
    padding: var(--rb-space-6);
  }
}
```

## ‚ö° Animation System
```css
:root {
  /* Transitions */
  --rb-transition-fast: 150ms ease-in-out;
  --rb-transition-base: 250ms ease-in-out;
  --rb-transition-slow: 350ms ease-in-out;
  
  /* Animations */
  --rb-animate-fade-in: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out;
  --rb-animate-slide-up: slideUp 0.3s ease-out;
  --rb-animate-bounce: bounce 0.5s ease-in-out;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes slideUp {
  from { 
    opacity: 0; 
    transform: translateY(20px); 
  }
  to { 
    opacity: 1; 
    transform: translateY(0); 
  }
}
```

